<pb n="0777a" xml:id="T16.0683.0777a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0777a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0777a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 683</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0777a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title><note type="orig" n="0777001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777001" type="mod">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0777001"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諸德福田經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="0777a04"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0777a05"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉沙門<note type="orig" n="0777002" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">（釋）＋法立【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777002">法立【大】，釋法立【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777002"><lem wit="【大】">法立</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">釋法立</rdg></app>、<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0777003" type="orig">法炬共譯＝共法炬譯【元】，法炬同譯【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0777003" resp="CBETA">法炬共譯【大】，共法炬譯【元】，法炬同譯【明】</note><app n="0777003"><lem wit="【大】">法炬共譯</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">共法炬譯</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">法炬同譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0777a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT16p0777a0601">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0777a0604">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="0777a07" ed="T"/>大<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0777004" type="orig">比丘＋（眾）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777004" type="mod" resp="CBETA">比丘【大】，比丘眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777004"><lem wit="【大】">比丘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">比丘眾</rdg></app>千二百五十，菩薩萬人，大眾無數圍
<lb ed="T" n="0777a08"/>繞說法。爾時天帝釋與諸欲天子三萬二千，
<lb ed="T" n="0777a09"/>各將營從不可稱數，來詣佛所，稽首于地，
<lb ed="T" n="0777a10"/>皆坐一面。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0777a1005"><note n="0777005" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔爾〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777005" type="mod" resp="CBETA">爾【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777005"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時天<note n="0777006" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">帝＋（釋）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777006">帝【大】，帝釋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777006"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">帝釋</rdg></app>察眾坐定，承佛神旨，
<lb n="0777a11" ed="T"/>從<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777007">坐而起＝座而興【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777007" type="mod">坐而起【大】，座而興【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777007"><lem wit="【大】">坐而起</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">座而興</rdg></app>，整<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0777008" type="orig">（衣）＋服【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777008" type="mod">服【大】，衣服【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777008"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">衣服</rdg></app>作禮，長跪叉手，白世尊
<lb ed="T" n="0777a12"/>曰：「欲有所問，唯願彰演，垂世軌則！」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0777a1214">佛告天
<lb n="0777a13" ed="T"/>帝：「譬如冥室，不求燈火，焉有所見？善哉問
<lb n="0777a14" ed="T"/>矣！吾當為汝分別說之。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0777a1410">天帝白佛：「夫人種
<lb n="0777a15" ed="T"/>德，欲求<note n="0777009" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">影＝景【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0777009" resp="CBETA">影【大】，景【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777009"><lem wit="【大】">影</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">景</rdg></app>福，豈有良田果報無限，種絲髮
<lb ed="T" n="0777a16"/>之德本，獲無量之福乎？唯願天尊敷揚<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777010">惠＝慧【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777010">惠【大】，慧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777010"><lem wit="【大】">惠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">慧</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0777a17"/>訓，令此愚<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0777011" type="orig">曚＝矇【宋】【宮】，蒙【元】【明】</note><note n="0777011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">曚【大】，矇【宋】【宮】，蒙【元】【明】</note><app n="0777011"><lem wit="【大】">曚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">矇</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蒙</rdg></app>福報無量！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1710" rend="inline">天尊歎曰：「<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777012">快＝善【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0777012" resp="CBETA">快【大】，善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777012"><lem wit="【大】">快</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善</rdg></app>哉，
<lb n="0777a18" ed="T"/>天帝！開意所問法無上矣！諦聽，善思！吾當
<lb ed="T" n="0777a19"/>具演，令汝歡喜。」天帝大眾受教而聽。</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1915" rend="inline">佛告
<lb ed="T" n="0777a20"/>天帝：「眾僧<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777013">〔之中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777013" type="mod">之中【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777013"><lem wit="【大】">之中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，有五淨德，名曰福田。供
<lb ed="T" n="0777a21"/>之得福，進可成佛。何謂為五？一者、發心離
<lb n="0777a22" ed="T"/>俗，懷佩道故；二者、毀其形好，應法服故；三者、
<lb ed="T" n="0777a23"/>永割親愛，無適莫故；四者、委棄軀命，遵<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777014">眾善＝崇道【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777014">眾善【大】，崇道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777014"><lem wit="【大】">眾
<lb n="0777a24" ed="T"/>善</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">崇道</rdg></app>故；五者、志求大乘，欲度人故。以此五<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0777015" type="orig">德＝福【宋】【元】，事【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777015" type="mod">德【大】，福【宋】【元】，事【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777015"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">福</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">事</rdg></app>，
<lb ed="T" n="0777a25"/>名曰福田；為良為美，為無<note n="0777016" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">早＝旱【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777016">早【大】，旱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777016"><lem wit="【大】">早</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">旱</rdg></app>喪；供之得福，
<lb ed="T" n="0777a26"/>難為喻矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a2605" rend="inline">爾時世尊以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0777a27"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777a2701" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「毀形守志節，</l><l>割愛無所親，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777a28"/><l>出家弘聖道，</l><l>願度一切人，</l>
<lb n="0777a29" ed="T"/><l>五德超世務，</l><l>名曰最福田，</l>
<pb n="0777b" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0777b"/>
<lb n="0777b01" ed="T"/><l>供養獲永安，</l><l>其福第一尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777b0201">佛告天帝：「復有七法廣施，名曰福田，行者
<lb n="0777b03" ed="T"/>得福，即生梵天。何謂為七？一者、興立佛圖、僧
<lb ed="T" n="0777b04"/>房、堂閣；二者、園果、浴池、樹木清涼；三者、常施
<lb ed="T" n="0777b05"/>醫藥，療救眾病；四者、作<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777017">牢堅＝堅牢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">牢堅【大】，堅牢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777017"><lem wit="【大】">牢堅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">堅牢</rdg></app>船，濟度人民；五
<lb n="0777b06" ed="T"/>者、安設橋梁，過度羸弱；六者、近道作井，渴乏
<lb n="0777b07" ed="T"/>得飲；七者、造作圊廁，施便利處。是為七事得
<lb ed="T" n="0777b08"/>梵天福。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777b0804" rend="inline">爾時世尊，以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0777b09"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT16p0777b0901"><l>「起塔立精舍，</l><l>園果施清涼，</l>
<lb n="0777b10" ed="T"/><l>病則醫藥救，</l><l>橋船度人民，</l>
<lb n="0777b11" ed="T"/><l>曠路作好井，</l><l>渴乏得安身，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777b12"/><l>所生食甘露，</l><l>無病常<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777018">安寧＝康寧【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777018" type="mod">安寧【大】，康寧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777018"><lem wit="【大】">安寧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">康寧</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777b13"/><l>造廁施清淨，</l><l>除穢致輕悅，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777b14"/><l>後無便利患，</l><l>莫見<note type="orig" n="0777019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">穢惡＝惡穢【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777019">穢惡【大】，惡穢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777019"><lem wit="【大】">穢惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡穢</rdg></app>者。</l>
<lb n="0777b15" ed="T"/><l>譬如五河流，</l><l>晝夜無休息，</l>
<lb n="0777b16" ed="T"/><l>此德亦如<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777020">斯＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777020" type="mod" resp="CBETA">斯【大】，是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777020"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>，</l><l>終得昇梵天。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777b1701">於時座中有一比丘，名曰聽聰，聞法欣悅，
<lb ed="T" n="0777b18"/>即從坐起，為佛作禮，長跪叉手，白世尊曰：
<lb ed="T" n="0777b19"/>「佛教真諦，洪潤無量。所以者何？我念宿命
<lb ed="T" n="0777b20"/>無數世時，<note n="0777021" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔生〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">生【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777021"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>波羅奈國，為長者子。於大道
<lb ed="T" n="0777b21"/>邊，作小精舍，床、臥、漿、<note n="0777022" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">糧＝𤄜【宋】【宮】，糒【元】【明】</note><note n="0777022" type="mod" resp="CBETA">糧【大】，𤄜【宋】【宮】，糒【元】【明】</note><app n="0777022"><lem wit="【大】">糧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">𤄜</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">糒</rdg></app>，供給眾僧；行路
<lb n="0777b22" ed="T"/>頓乏，亦得止息。緣此功德，命終生天，為天帝
<lb n="0777b23" ed="T"/>釋，下生世間，為轉輪聖王，各三十六<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0777023">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777023" type="mod">反【大】，返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777023"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">返</rdg></app>，典
<lb n="0777b24" ed="T"/>領天、人，足下生毛，躡虛而遊，九十一劫，食
<lb n="0777b25" ed="T"/>福自然。今值世尊，顧臨眾生，蠲我愚濁，安
<lb ed="T" n="0777b26"/>以淨慧，生死栽枯，號曰真人，福報誠諦，其
<lb ed="T" n="0777b27"/>為然矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777b2704" rend="inline">爾時聽聰以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0777b28"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777b2801" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「<note n="0777024" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宋】【明】</note><note n="0777024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">惟【大】，唯【宋】【明】</note><app n="0777024"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">唯</rdg></app>念過去世，</l><l>供養為輕微，</l>
<lb n="0777b29" ed="T"/><l>蒙報歷遐劫，</l><l>餘福值天師。</l>
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0777c" n="0777c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0777c01"/><l>淨慧斷生死，</l><l>癡愛<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777025">情＝消【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777025">情【大】，消【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777025"><lem wit="【大】">情</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">消</rdg></app>無遺，</l>
<lb n="0777c02" ed="T"/><l>佛恩流無窮，</l><l>是故重自歸。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0777c03"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777c0301">於<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777026">時＝是【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777026" type="mod">時【大】，是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777026"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>聽聰禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名<note n="0777027" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">曰【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777027"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0777c04" ed="T"/>波拘盧，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0777028" type="orig">（即）＋從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">從【大】，即從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777028"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">即從</rdg></app>座而起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0777c05" ed="T"/>世尊曰：「我念宿命，生拘夷那竭國，為長者
<lb ed="T" n="0777c06"/>子。時世無佛，眾僧教化，大會說法，我往聽
<lb ed="T" n="0777c07"/>經。聞法歡喜，持一藥果，名<note type="orig" n="0777029" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">呵梨勒＝阿梨勒【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0777029" resp="CBETA">呵梨勒【大】，阿梨勒【明】</note><app n="0777029"><lem wit="【大】">呵梨勒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">阿梨勒</rdg></app>，奉上
<lb n="0777c08" ed="T"/>眾僧。緣此果報，命終<note type="orig" n="0777030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">昇＝生【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777030">昇【大】，生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777030"><lem wit="【大】">昇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">生</rdg></app>天，下生世間，恒
<lb ed="T" n="0777c09"/>處尊貴，端正雄傑，與眾超絕，九十一劫，未
<lb ed="T" n="0777c10"/>曾<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777031">有＝疾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">有【大】，疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777031"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">疾</rdg></app>病。餘福值佛，光導癡冥，授我法藥，逮
<lb ed="T" n="0777c11"/>得應真，力能移山，慧能消惡。善哉福報，為
<lb ed="T" n="0777c12"/>真諦矣！」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0777c1204">爾時波拘盧以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0777c13" ed="T"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT16p0777c1301"><l>「慈澤潤枯槁，</l><l>德勳濟苦<note type="orig" n="0777032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">患＝勤【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0777032" resp="CBETA">患【大】，勤【宮】</note><app n="0777032"><lem wit="【大】">患</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">勤</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777c14"/><l>一果之善本，</l><l>享福迄今存。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0777c15"/><l>佛垂真諦義，</l><l>蒙教超出淵，</l>
<lb n="0777c16" ed="T"/><l>聖眾祐無極，</l><l>稽首上福田。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777c1701">於時波拘盧禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名曰
<lb ed="T" n="0777c18"/>須陀耶，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0777c19" ed="T"/>世尊曰：「我自<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0777033" type="orig">惟＝唯【明】下同</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777033" type="mod">惟【大】下同，唯【明】下同</note><app n="0777033"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>念先世之時，生維耶離國，
<lb n="0777c20" ed="T"/>為小<note type="orig" n="0777034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">家＝民家作【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777034" type="mod">家【大】，民家作【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777034"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">民家作</rdg></app>子。時世無佛，眾僧<note n="0777035" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0777035" type="mod">行【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777035"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>教化。我時
<lb ed="T" n="0777c21"/>持酪，入市欲賣，值遇眾僧，大會講法，過而
<lb ed="T" n="0777c22"/>立聽，法言微妙，聞<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777036">之＝則【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777036" type="mod" resp="CBETA">之【大】，則【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777036"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>歡悅，即舉瓶酪，布
<lb ed="T" n="0777c23"/>施眾僧。眾僧呪願，益懷欣<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777037">踊＝勇【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777037">踊【大】＊，勇【宮】＊</note><app n="0777037"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">勇</rdg></app>。緣此福<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0777038">報＝德【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0777038">報【大】，德【宮】</note><app n="0777038"><lem wit="【大】">報</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>，
<lb ed="T" n="0777c24"/><note type="orig" n="0777039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">壽終生天＝終生天上【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777039" type="mod" resp="CBETA">壽終生天【大】，終生天上【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777039"><lem wit="【大】">壽終生天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">終生天上</rdg></app>，下<note type="orig" n="0777040" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">生＝在【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777040" type="mod" resp="CBETA">生【大】，在【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777040"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">在</rdg></app>世間，財富無限，九十一
<lb ed="T" n="0777c25"/>劫，<note type="orig" n="0777041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">豪尊榮貴＝豪貴尊榮【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0777041" resp="CBETA">豪尊榮貴【大】，豪貴尊榮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777041"><lem wit="【大】">豪尊榮貴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">豪貴尊榮</rdg></app>。末後餘愆，生於世間，母妊
<lb n="0777c26" ed="T"/>數月，得病命終，埋母塚中，月滿乃生。塚中
<lb n="0777c27" ed="T"/>七年，飲死母乳，用自濟活。微福值佛，開闡
<lb n="0777c28" ed="T"/>明法，超度死地，逮得應真。諦哉罪福，誠如
<lb n="0777c29" ed="T"/>佛教！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777c2903" rend="inline">爾時須陀耶以偈頌曰：</p>
<pb n="0778a" xml:id="T16.0683.0778a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778a01" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778a0101" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「前為小家子，</l><l>賣酪以自存，</l>
<lb n="0778a02" ed="T"/><l>欣<app type="star" corresp="#0777037"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">勇</rdg></app>施微薄，</l><l>得離三苦患。</l>
<lb n="0778a03" ed="T"/><l>雖罪塚中生，</l><l>飲乳活七年，</l>
<lb n="0778a04" ed="T"/><l>因緣得解脫，</l><l>歸命聖福田。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0778a05"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778a0501">於時須陀耶禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名曰
<lb ed="T" n="0778a06"/><note type="orig" n="0778001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778001" resp="CBETA">阿【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0778001"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>難，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb ed="T" n="0778a07"/>世尊曰：「我念宿命，生羅閱祇<note n="0778002" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔國〕－【宮】</note><note n="0778002" type="mod" resp="CBETA">國【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0778002"><lem wit="【大】">國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，為庶民子，
<lb n="0778a08" ed="T"/>身生惡瘡，治之不差。有親友道人，來語我
<lb n="0778a09" ed="T"/>言：『當浴眾僧，取其浴水，以用<note n="0778003" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">洗＝洒【宮】＊</note><note n="0778003" type="mod" resp="CBETA">洗【大】＊，洒【宮】＊</note><app n="0778003"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">洒</rdg></app>瘡，便可
<lb n="0778a10" ed="T"/><note type="orig" n="0778004" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">除＝得【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778004">除【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778004"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>愈，又可得福！』我即歡喜，往到寺中，加
<lb n="0778a11" ed="T"/>敬至心，更作新井、香油浴具，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778005" type="orig">洗＝洒【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778005" type="mod">洗【大】，洒【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0778005"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">洒</rdg></app>浴眾僧，以
<lb ed="T" n="0778a12"/>汁<app corresp="#0778003" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">洒</rdg></app>瘡，尋蒙除愈。從此因緣，所生端正，金
<lb n="0778a13" ed="T"/>色晃昱，不受塵垢，九十一劫，常得淨福，僧
<lb ed="T" n="0778a14"/>祐廣遠。今<note n="0778006" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">復＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778006" type="mod" resp="CBETA">復【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778006"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>值佛，心垢消滅，逮得應真。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0778a1416">阿
<lb n="0778a15" ed="T"/>難於佛前以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778a16" ed="T"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT16p0778a1601"><l>「聖眾為良<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0778007">醫＝藥【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778007">醫【大】，藥【宮】</note><app n="0778007"><lem wit="【大】">醫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">藥</rdg></app>，</l><l>救濟苦惱患，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778a17"/><l><app type="star" corresp="#0778003"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">洒</rdg></app>浴施清淨，</l><l>瘡愈蒙得安。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778a18"/><l>所生常端正，</l><l>殊異紫金顏，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778a19"/><l><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778008" type="orig">德＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778008" type="mod" resp="CBETA">德【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778008"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>潤無<note type="orig" n="0778009" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">崖＝涯【元】【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0778009" resp="CBETA">崖【大】，涯【元】【明】</note><app n="0778009"><lem wit="【大】">崖</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">涯</rdg></app>限，</l><l>歸命良福田。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0778a20"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778a2001"><note n="0778010" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">（於時）＋阿難【元】【明】，〔阿〕－【宮】</note><note n="0778010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">阿難【大】，於時阿難【元】【明】，難【宮】</note><app n="0778010"><lem wit="【大】">阿難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">於時阿難</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">難</rdg></app>禮已還坐。爾時座中有一比丘尼，名
<lb n="0778a21" ed="T"/>曰奈女，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb ed="T" n="0778a22"/>佛言：「<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778011" type="orig">我＋（自）【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778011" type="mod">我【大】，我自【宮】</note><app n="0778011"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">我自</rdg></app>念先世，生波羅奈國，為貧女人。時
<lb n="0778a23" ed="T"/>世有佛，名曰迦葉，時與大眾，圍繞說法。我
<lb ed="T" n="0778a24"/>時在座，聞經歡喜，意欲布施，顧無所有，自
<lb n="0778a25" ed="T"/>惟貧賤，心用悲感，詣他園圃，乞求果<note n="0778012" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">蓏＝菜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">蓏【大】，菜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778012"><lem wit="【大】">蓏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">菜</rdg></app>，當
<lb ed="T" n="0778a26"/>以施佛。時得一奈，大而香好，擎一<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0778013">盂＝鉢【宋】【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778013">盂【大】，鉢【宋】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778013"><lem wit="【大】">盂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鉢</rdg></app>水、并
<lb n="0778a27" ed="T"/>奈一枚，奉迦葉佛，及諸眾僧。佛知至意，呪願
<lb n="0778a28" ed="T"/>受之，分布水、奈，一切周普。緣此福<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778014" type="orig">祚＝德【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778014">祚【大】，德【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778014"><lem wit="【大】">祚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>，壽盡
<lb ed="T" n="0778a29"/>生天，得為天后。下生世間，不由胞胎，九十
<pb n="0778b" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0778b"/>
<lb n="0778b01" ed="T"/>一劫，生奈華中，端正鮮<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778015" type="orig">淨＝好【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">淨【大】，好【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778015"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">好</rdg></app>，常識宿命。今值
<lb n="0778b02" ed="T"/>世尊，開示道眼。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0778b0207">爾時奈女以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778b03" ed="T"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT16p0778b0301"><l>「三尊慈潤普，</l><l>慧度無男女，</l>
<lb n="0778b04" ed="T"/><l>水果施弘報，</l><l>緣得離眾苦。</l>
<lb n="0778b05" ed="T"/><l>在世生華中，</l><l>上則為天后，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778b06"/><l>自歸聖眾祐，</l><l>福田最深厚。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b0701"><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0778016">（於是）＋比【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778016">比【大】，於是比【元】【明】</note><app n="0778016"><lem wit="【大】">比</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">於是比</rdg></app>丘尼奈女禮已還坐。於<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0778017">時＝是【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0778017" type="mod" resp="CBETA"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->時【大】＊，是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0778017"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>天帝即從座
<lb n="0778b08" ed="T"/>起，為佛作禮，白世尊曰：「我先世時，生拘留
<lb ed="T" n="0778b09"/>大國，為長者子。青衣抱行，入城遊觀，值遇
<lb ed="T" n="0778b10"/>眾僧，街巷分衛。時見人民，施者甚多，即自
<lb n="0778b11" ed="T"/>念言：『願得財寶，布施眾僧，不亦快乎！』即解
<lb n="0778b12" ed="T"/><note type="orig" n="0778018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">珠瓔＝珠纓【宋】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778018" resp="CBETA">珠瓔【大】，珠纓【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0778018"><lem wit="【大】">珠瓔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">珠纓</rdg></app>，布施眾僧。同心呪願，歡喜而去。從
<lb n="0778b13" ed="T"/>此因緣，壽終即生忉利天上，為天帝釋，九
<lb n="0778b14" ed="T"/>十一劫，永離八難。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778b1408" rend="inline">於<note n="0778b1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">是【CB】【麗-CB】，時【大】</note><app n="0778b1401"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say">是<note type="cf1">K12n0366_p0156c17</note><note type="cf2">T16n0683_p0778b24</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">時</rdg></app><anchor xml:id="fxT16p0778b01"/>天帝以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0778b15"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778b1501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「德高無過者，</l><l>開福塞禍<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778019" type="orig">元＝原【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778019" resp="CBETA">元【大】，原【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778019"><lem wit="【大】">元</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">原</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0778b16" ed="T"/><l>聖眾神<note n="0778020" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">定＝足【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778020" type="mod">定【大】，足【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778020"><lem wit="【大】">定</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">足</rdg></app>力，</l><l>童幼發歡喜。</l>
<lb n="0778b17" ed="T"/><l>效眾悅意施，</l><l>遷神典二天，</l>
<lb n="0778b18" ed="T"/><l>自歸<note type="orig" n="0778021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">世最厚＝聖眾祐【元】【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0778021" resp="CBETA">世最厚【大】，聖眾祐【元】【明】</note><app n="0778021"><lem wit="【大】">世最厚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">聖眾祐</rdg></app>，</l><l>世世願奉尊。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0778b19"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b1901">佛告天帝及諸大眾：「聽我<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0778022">所＝自【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778022" type="mod">所【大】，自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778022"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg></app>說，宿命所行。
<lb ed="T" n="0778b20"/>昔我前世於波羅奈國，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778023" type="orig">近＝在【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778023" type="mod">近【大】，在【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778023"><lem wit="【大】">近</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>大道邊，安施圊
<lb ed="T" n="0778b21"/>廁，國中人<note n="0778024" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">民＝眾【宮】</note><note n="0778024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">民【大】，眾【宮】</note><app n="0778024"><lem wit="【大】">民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">眾</rdg></app>，得輕安者，莫不感義。緣此功
<lb n="0778b22" ed="T"/>德，所生<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0778025" type="orig">淨＝清【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778025" resp="CBETA">淨【大】，清【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778025"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清</rdg></app>潔，累劫<note type="orig" n="0778026" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">行＝修【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778026" type="mod">行【大】，修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778026"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">修</rdg></app>道，穢染不污，功祚
<lb ed="T" n="0778b23"/>大備，自致成佛。金<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778027" type="orig">體光耀＝色光曜【宋】【宮】，色晃晃【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778027">體光耀【大】，色光曜【宋】【宮】，色晃晃【元】【明】</note><app n="0778027"><lem wit="【大】">體光耀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">色光曜</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">色晃晃</rdg></app>，塵水不著，食
<lb ed="T" n="0778b24"/>自消化，無便利之患。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778b2409" rend="inline">於是世尊以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778b25" ed="T"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT16p0778b2501"><l>「忍<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778028" type="orig">穢＝辱【宋】【元】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778028" type="mod">穢【大】，辱【宋】【元】</note><app n="0778028"><lem wit="【大】">穢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">辱</rdg></app>修福事，</l><l><note n="0778b2501" resp="CBETA" type="add">為【CB】【麗-CB】，我【大】</note><app n="0778b2501"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say">為<note type="cf1">K12n0366_p0157a05</note><note type="cf2">T12n0387_p1095a08</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">我</rdg></app>人所不污，</l>
<lb n="0778b26" ed="T"/><l>造廁施便利，</l><l>煩重得輕安。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778b27"/><l>此德除貢高，</l><l>因解生死緣，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0778b28"/><l>進<note n="0778029" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">登＝發【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778029" type="mod">登【大】，發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778029"><lem wit="【大】">登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">發</rdg></app>成佛道，</l><l>空淨巍巍尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b2901">佛告天帝：「九十六種道，佛道最尊；九十六
<pb n="0778c" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0778c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0778c01"/>種法，<note type="orig" n="0778030" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">（以）＋佛【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778030">佛【大】，以佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778030"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以佛</rdg></app>法最真；九十六種僧，佛僧最正。所
<lb ed="T" n="0778c02"/>以者何？如來從阿僧祇劫發願誠諦，殞命積
<lb n="0778c03" ed="T"/>德，誓為眾生，國財、妻子、頭目、血肉，以用布
<lb n="0778c04" ed="T"/>施，無戀愛之心；心若虛空，無所不覆，六度、
<lb n="0778c05" ed="T"/>四等眾善普備，德慧成滿，乃得為佛；身色
<lb n="0778c06" ed="T"/>紫金，相好無比，去來現在無不<note type="orig" n="0778031" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">照＝昭【宋】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778031" resp="CBETA">照【大】，昭【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0778031"><lem wit="【大】">照</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">昭</rdg></app>達，三界
<lb n="0778c07" ed="T"/>尊天莫能及者；言信德重，震動天地。其有
<lb n="0778c08" ed="T"/>眾生，<note type="orig" n="0778032" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">發一＝一發【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778032" resp="CBETA">發一【大】，一發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778032"><lem wit="【大】">發一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一發</rdg></app>敬心<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778033" type="orig">向＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">向【大】，於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778033"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>如來者，勝獲大千世界
<lb ed="T" n="0778c09"/>之珍寶矣！說三十七品、十二部經，分別罪
<lb ed="T" n="0778c10"/>福，言皆至誠，開三乘教，各得奉行，聞者歡
<lb n="0778c11" ed="T"/>喜，樂作沙門，信佛行法，志尚清高。眾僧之
<lb n="0778c12" ed="T"/>中，有四雙八輩、十二賢者，捨世貪諍，導世
<lb ed="T" n="0778c13"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778034" type="orig">開＝間【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0778034" resp="CBETA">開【大】，間【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778034"><lem wit="【大】">開</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">間</rdg></app>福，天、人路通，眾僧之由矣。是為最尊無
<lb n="0778c14" ed="T"/>上之<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0778035">道＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0778035">道【大】，道也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778035"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">道也</rdg></app>，諸佛、菩薩、緣覺、應真皆從中出，教
<lb ed="T" n="0778c15"/>化一切，度脫群生。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778c1508" rend="inline">佛說是時，天帝釋眾皆
<lb ed="T" n="0778c16"/>發無上正真道意，不可計人得法眼淨。於是
<lb ed="T" n="0778c17"/>阿難長跪叉手，白<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0778036" type="orig">佛＝世尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778036" type="mod" resp="CBETA">佛【大】，世尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778036"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世尊</rdg></app>言：「此名何經？云何奉
<lb n="0778c18" ed="T"/><note type="orig" n="0778037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">持＝行【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778037" type="mod">持【大】，行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778037"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">行</rdg></app>？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0778c1802">佛告阿難：「是經名曰『諸德福田』，<note n="0778038" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">常＝當【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0778038" type="mod">常【大】，當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0778038"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當</rdg></app>奉持
<lb n="0778c19" ed="T"/>之，明宣經道，莫令缺減！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778c1910" rend="inline">佛說經已，天帝釋
<lb ed="T" n="0778c20"/>眾、一切眾會，莫不歡喜，作禮而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="T" n="0778c21"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="001"><cb:jhead><title><app type="star" corresp="#0777001"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諸德福田經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>